  "instructions": [
    "Place the tortilla on a flat surface and spread the chickpea spread evenly over the center of the tortilla.",
    "Add the roasted eggplant, red bell pepper, parsley, cilantro, herbes-de-provence, garlic powder, salt, and black pepper on top of the chickpea spread.",
    "Add the steam-tolerant greens on top of the vegetables.",
    "Add a sprinkle of chopped scallions on top of the greens.",
    "Drizzle the fresh lemon juice over the top of the wrap.",
    "Fold the bottom half of the tortilla up over the filling, then fold in the sides and roll the wrap up tightly.",
    "Place the wrap in a steamer basket and steam for 10-12 minutes, or until the tortilla is soft and the filling is heated through.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
